Scenario A: Dust Storm Degradation

Â· Simulate increasing dust density D over time
Â· Baseline: Stereo vision fails, rover stops or drives blind
Â· SAPNA: Vision weight w_cam decreases, IMU/radar weight increases; rover continues at reduced speed
Â· Success criterion: State estimation error remains below 5% of traveled distance

