Â· Deformable sandy slope with high slip ratio
Â· Baseline: Wheel odometry overestimates progress, leading to pathâ€‘following errors
Â· SAPNA: Cognitive layer detects slip, inflates R_odo, relies on visual odometry; fuzzy logic prevents rapid weight oscillation
Â· Success criterion: No oscillation in weights; stable state estimation

