Â· Success criterion: Î”E_motion_saved > Î”E_computation_spent

7.4 Digital Twin Validation with Monte Carlo Analysis

A digital twin of the rover (including sensor models, dynamics, and onboard software) runs on a representative processor. This enables:

Â· Repeatable testing of extreme conditions
Â· Measurement of realâ€‘time computational performance
Â· Verification of stability under edge cases
Â· Monte Carlo sensitivity analysis: Running 10,000+ simulations with randomized dust, gravity, illumination, and slip parameters to prove that SAPNA's worstâ€‘case performance exceeds the baseline's nominal performance

7.5 Field Testing

